net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component

Interface TabItem


  • public interface TabItem
    Indicates a component provides a default TabItemDisplay for use in a TabbedContainer. Convenience for packaging the tab content with an item that defines the default display in the tab for that content.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@proteus.co)
